{"tid":1666124,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴：蘇帥可以一直談未來 我也想找這樣的工作","createTime":"2019-10-21T00:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T05:44:10.000Z","uid":25345,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c20abdde3d24c6b0c6fb061dddb6ed3cc6a5611d","tid":1666124,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:22:55.000Z","msg":"新賽季，曼聯在蘇斯克查治下戰績不佳，但蘇帥在媒體面前一直表現得非常樂觀。如今在雙紅會前，前曼聯教練摩連奴也開起了蘇帥的玩笑。<br />\n<br />\n  摩帥稱：「曼聯在這周做了很好的公關工作，讓事情變得非常清楚，也為比賽營造了積極的氛圍。我要試著找一份奧萊（蘇斯克查）這樣的工作，可以一直談論未來的這種。」<br />\n<br />\n  「這是一個很好的情況，簽下三年合約，可以討論未來、年輕的球員。我認為在這樣的豪門能這麼做，真是太棒了。」"},{"pid":"3afea7a57efe37f86b06c033f9eeb3a873867cfb","tid":1666124,"uid":73356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:25:22.000Z","msg":"暗示要去未來熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52afc45f95878e036691e8d7af1a4190317016f","tid":1666124,"uid":66839,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:58:48.000Z","msg":"收皮啦摩狗<br />\n<br />\n買山狗返黎談咩未來"},{"pid":"5ca79c7919da564b5aa7ab71c37563b5deee3eac","tid":1666124,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:11:28.000Z","msg":"so9既未來唔知有冇三年"},{"pid":"7574c52d5e4a8261cc2164fde73addf9702423b3","tid":1666124,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:12:46.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係摩佬+熱狗"},{"pid":"1ae9337e615ad72bcffed291af75b157a9fe2b2e","tid":1666124,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d52afc45f95878e036691e8d7af1a4190317016f","tid":1666124,"uid":66839,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:58:48.000Z","msg":"收皮啦摩狗<br />\n<br />\n買山狗返黎談咩未來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:56:48.000Z","msg":"就係串之前曼無俾機會談未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e43caf9d32704714956be42345ecd9148d5f6b","tid":1666124,"uid":184952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ae9337e615ad72bcffed291af7